msgid "Choose the non-kidnapper [[Suspect]] enemies that were defeated:"
msgstr "選擇被擊敗的非綁架犯的[[嫌犯]]敵人："

msgid "Brian Burnham is out for blood."
msgstr "布里安·伯納姆要你血債血償。"

